definition.value: A monoterpene that is octa-1,6-diene bearing methylene and methyl substituents at positions 3 and 7 respectively.
A UDP-amino sugar that is UDP-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine having an beta-D-galactose-1-phospho moiety attached at position 6.
A hydroxycoumarin that is umbelliferone substituted by a methyl group at position 4.
